resources.string: Prayer Time Alarm is an Android Apps that takes Alarm in Five Prayer Time. The Alarm will be start at the begening of two Prayer(Fazar and Magrib) time and Zuhor start at 12.45 pm and next two Prayer (Asar,Easha) time will be start after 15 minute from the begening Time.Fazar and Magrib alarm start due time because it can be effect in Ramadan.
